description: Hill Country BBQ is the Best Tex-Mex and BBQ outside of Austin!It all started with a Texas boy's passion for food and smiles shared only with his dearest, and grew into a demand for more mouth-watering cooking. The word spread quickly and we began cooking for friend's parties and their guests also fell in love... Hill Country Catering was born. We specialize in real Texas-style barbeque and authentic Tex-Mex cuisine. We use only the freshest meats and ingredients, family recipes and heart and soul from our kitchen to you. So whether you are entertaining for 25 or 500, we will help make your event one that your guests will never forget!
name: Hill Country BBQ
